Depends: python, python-lxml, python-pillow, python-psutil, rust, make, pkg-config, cmake
Section: recon
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://maigret.readthedocs.io
Description: OSINT username search tool with 3000+ sites
 Maigret collects information about a given username across
 thousands of social networks and websites. It provides
 detailed reports and supports recursive searching.
